_sText: This is only my second map. I found out how to make ladders so I just had to make stuff with ladders. Also I found out how to do some secrets so I added one. All in all its a fun deathmatch map. I figured I would make my first texture. This is my first real map because my first first map was just a map on me learning the basics. I hope you will comment on my map! Also provide some feedback and errors I may have made.
